author: fwyzard
body:
Follow up to #19891 and #19912.

Merge the following HLT DQM pull requests (in this order):
  - #19490 from bpf6qc:METplusTrackOfflineDQM92X
  - #19499 from gomber:DarkSUSY
  - #19596 from jmduarte:met-mht-b-tag-dqm-93x
  - #19694 from jingyuluo:DisplacedJet_DQM_for93X_new
  - #19703 from antoniovagnerini:from-CMSSW_9_2_1-trigger17-dqm-rebased
  - #19627 from gkaratha:dqm_topMonitoring_doublemu3pfmet50pfmhet60
  - #19781 from marinakolosova:TOPandBTVchanges

and address the issues raised in the discussion of #19499, #19267.
title: HLT DQM for 9.3.x - part 4
